# ── Docker build context = REPO ROOT ────────────────────────────────────────
# backend-a/ and backend-b/ each set  image_build_context ".."  so their images
# can COPY the shared semantius CLI from linux-x64/. That makes the whole repo
# the build context, so exclude everything heavy or irrelevant here — the images
# only ever COPY  linux-x64/  and  backend-a/skills/ .
**/node_modules
**/.wrangler
**/.flue-vite
**/dist
**/dist-bundle
.git
.claude
.agents
.patch-ds
frontend
core
scripts
patches
*.tsbuildinfo
.api-token
